data.description: This must see townhome has beautiful luxury vinyl planks throughout the home in addition to granite counter tops in the kitchen and breakfast nook.  This is the place for entertaining!  Great open concept floorplan!  Walk right out to your patio from the dining room!  There is lots of extra space in the finished basement, perfect for those out of town guests!  Upgraded lighting and light fixtures throughout this home, the list goes on and on!  The owners have spared no expense in updating this gorgeous home!  Just steps away from Utah park and pool!  Come and see it for yourself!
